title: What are your strengths and weaknesses in League?
body:
Everyone has some, regardless of elo. For your own elo purposes, what do you excel at and what's your weakest link?

Here's mine:

Strengths: Support main, with a good variety. Positive attitude, and I enjoy chatting before and after the game. Can fill most roles reliably if needed. 

Weaknesses: Jungling(Not terrible at it, but not good either). Dragon control. Matchup knowledge in other roles. Little variety in other roles.
